abstract: Jimmy Walker wins Texas Open with two-under-par 70; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: With a two-under-par 70, Jimmy Walker won the Texas Open in San Antonio to become the first two-time winner this season on the PGA Tour, beating Jordan Spieth, who also closed with a 70, by four strokes.
